        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 报名表单区域 -->
  <section id="报名表单" class="py-24 scroll-mt-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <!-- 左侧：课程优势 -->
        <div class="scroll-animate">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-cyan bg-cyan/10 rounded-full mb-4">
              立即报名
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-6">
              开始您的太极之旅
            </h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-cyan/50 mb-8"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
            <p class="text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
              填写右侧报名表单，我们的课程顾问将在<span class="text-accent font-medium">24小时内</span>与您联系，为您推荐最适合的课程。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- 上课时间 -->
          <div class="bg-mist/20 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="mr-2">📅</span>
              上课时间
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-secondary">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></div>
                <span>工作日班：周一至周五 上午9:00-11:00，下午14:00-16:00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan"></div>
                <span>周末班：周六、周日 上午9:00-11:00，下午14:00-16:00</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary"></div>
                <span>晚班：周一至周五 19:00-21:00</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 课程价格 -->
          <div class="bg-mist/20 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="mr-2">💰</span>
              课程价格
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-secondary">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span>24式太极拳入门班</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-ink">¥1,200/期</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span>42式太极拳进阶班</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-ink">¥1,800/期</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span>传统108式研修班</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-ink">¥2,800/期</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span>一对一私教课程</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-ink">¥300/小时</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/30">
              * 新学员首次体验课仅需 ¥99，满意后再报名
