      <p class="text-xl text-secondary mb-12">
        新学员首次体验课仅需 ¥99
      </p>
      <a
        href="#报名表单"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-primary text-paper hover:text-paper border-2 border-accent hover:border-primary rounded-lg font-medium text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        立即报名
      </a>
